snippet.title: Phantom Blade Zero Gameplay Trailer - SGF2024
snippet.description: New trailer of Phantom Blade Zero, giving a sneak peek to the latest development of the game, featuring never-shown-before footages depicting high-speed combat and multiple weapons, among other gameplay elements. Announcement of a world tour demo.
